divs: Sighting Details1. I was in my sunroom 2. I notice these objects around 6:40 to 10:30 pm at night 3. These objects slowly hover above the city, not following the sideral path of the stars. 4. These objects flicker and change shape, but amazingly, no one takes a look above them in Windsor to notice. 5. No feelings except curiosity. 6. These objects disappear around 10:30 at night, but sometimes show up again in the morning.
Summary: Series of different UFOs which light up at different times.
trends: There have been 18 other sightings in Windsor
